==English==

===[[Intransitive verb]]===
'''to network'''  ([[networks]], [[networked]], [[networking]])
# To [[interact]] [[social]]ly for the purpose of getting connections or personal [[advance]]ment
#:''Many people find it worthwhile to '''network''' for jobs and information.''

===[[Transitive verb]]===
'''to network'''  ([[networks]], [[networked]], [[networking]])
# To connect two or more [[computer]]s or other computerized devices
#:''If we '''network''' his machine to the server, he will be able to see all the files.''
# To [[interconenect]] a [[group]] or [[system]]

